{"tid":1370493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無民權政府 無party politics 係永遠冇「獨立」可言","createTime":"2019-07-27T04:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T04:40:31.000Z","uid":126889,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"066b5456b0afb8ed7dae2afa32683156b3229332","tid":1370493,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:22:51.000Z","msg":"最有可能既情況下，政府會成立個「獨立」調整委員會，但係放左好多自己友入去，拎班人出黎祭旗，反正班人本來就預左拎黎祭旗，大家有口叫condom。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家仲好快大家就會階段性勝利，政權續命。<br />\n<br />\n委員會係必須有，前提係係由民選政府成立。<br />\n<br />\n依家由港共政府成立既任何「獨立」既野都係糖衣毒藥。<br />\n<br />\n我奉勸大家唔好開口埋口都係話人係鬼，世界冇咁多鬼，研究下可能性可以，但唔係個個連登仔都有咁好既政治知識同思考能力。黎到依一刻其實個個都自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51dfb0afb5dac7b6120cc6fb5b8b551bdd9c74d8","tid":1370493,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"亦唔好信有咩好人好法官，依個政府咩都做得出"},{"pid":"9f3642fae40b75677d7f889bd92079e1f5619bd4","tid":1370493,"uid":126889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:26:24.000Z","msg":"721晚個面皮就已經撕破 唔好對個制度有幻想會對大家有好處"},{"pid":"83cdd704501e7d6b38eb366a962363468f5b4e79","tid":1370493,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:26:34.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"5b895cef26b616245147181c4ca01207a9a9e0a1","tid":1370493,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時連登開po 冇咩三毛既keyword 都有人睇？"},{"pid":"f2e8ff61fb94e9a00a116eeeb97709fd70c88d08","tid":1370493,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8060c82bfa16eee1bf579d